# DETECTION CRITERIA

**Bull Trending**: Price >EMA200, higher highs/lows, RSI 50-70, volume growing
**Bull Euphoric**: RSI >75, funding >0.10%, extreme sentiment, parabolic moves
**Bear**: Price <EMA200, lower highs/lows, RSI <40
**Range**: Price oscillating 10-20% range, declining volume, RSI 40-60
**High Vol**: ATR >5% daily, Bollinger bandwidth >10%, erratic swings

